Manage > Atom > shared web server > base url > override > put the public ip > api type : intermediate > auth : basic > protected headers: use default > save > restart plugin > user management > generate token

Go to flow > create the flow integration service > imp : url will be shared-web-server-ip and port followed by flow services path

flow services path will be found in the integration > build > flow services component.... example /fs/flow-service-testing

so the overall url in the flow service definition will be... example http://13.58.69.44:9090/fs/flow-service-testing

